data.description: Nestled in quiet Shannon Lakes, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home is a hidden gem waiting for your personal touch.  The first floor is open and spacious offering a flex room perfect for an office or den.  The second floor has 4 large bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  The second floor laundry is spacious and convenient. This is an opportunity to create something truly special and make a lasting mark in a fantastic community. Don't miss out on this one!
